{"tid":522224,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"手機嚴寒環境生存秘技","createTime":"2018-01-07T10:40:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-07T14:04:53.000Z","uid":66607,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d594cbf57a20a9ffe52354e209193657e6495356","tid":522224,"uid":66607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T10:40:13.000Z","msg":"講到尾，部電話隨時仲弱過人類，不過無計又真係驚凍<br />\n<br />\n如果必須要將手機放在室外，就可能需要購買特製的防寒手機保護套，這些保護套擁有夾層，可以做到防風防寒，不怕手機被凍傷。專家亦建議不要在嚴寒環境下為智能手機充電，Apple 亦警告用戶在極端低溫下為 iPhone 充電，有機會造成損壞，所以還是在室內較溫暖的環境下才為手機充電比較理想。以 iPhone 為例，Apple 表示手機的正常運作環境為攝氏 0 至 35 度，不過當關機後，手機則可以捱過攝氏 -20 至 45 的溫度，所以不想手機在嚴寒中受損，或許關機會是最佳的方法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4247/209847/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4247%2F209847%2F1%2F&d=eFWhHJ%2FCccjbr1mpHvZQxJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=c8efdcff\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4247/209847/1/</a>"},{"pid":"957ebd859e809b27b60f51b4ebd7609ecc10ccf4","tid":522224,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T10:44:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"94d02cc5e6dac30d0c315ca4aef82e36d2b2116d","tid":522224,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"957ebd859e809b27b60f51b4ebd7609ecc10ccf4","tid":522224,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T10:44:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T11:10:43.000Z","msg":"擺係個春袋下面"},{"pid":"1f0217e08f3d4190e3d7012864ec7c2a27560d22","tid":522224,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T14:04:53.000Z","msg":"係香港，過熱會唔會實際d，其實好容易過35度"}]}